# Public-share staging directory (snapshot of HEAD with a fresh README).
# Built by hand with git archive; not part of the repo's history.
To Post/

# Texture encode cache (basisu ktx2 keyed by content hash). Per-clone,
# can grow to hundreds of MiB on textured scenes; do not check in. Folder
# itself is tracked (via model_cache/.gitignore) so the path exists on
# fresh clones; only the contents are ignored.
model_cache/*
!model_cache/.gitignore

